==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overestimate
<hw>O`ver*es"ti*mate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>To estimate too highly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <def>To overvalue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overestimate</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overestimate
<hw>O`ver*es"ti*mate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An estimate
that is too high; <as>as, an <ex>overestimate</ex> of the
vote</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overexcite</ent>⟦br⟧
